1. Create server.js
2. pnpm init
   That will create package.json
3. Create .gitignore and place there at least /node_modules
4. Then:
   pnpm install socket.io
   pnpm install express
   pnpm install nodemon
5. Add following in package.json - "scripts" section
   "agar": "nodemon AGARCLONE/server.mjs"

Point 5 changed to:
   "agar": "nodemon index.mjs"
in final version.
